{"tid":1864213,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於溝到女神","createTime":"2020-02-05T13:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T20:42:26.000Z","uid":54342,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2a773d023d314276f369e85f55b1d46610f018","tid":1864213,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"話說今日係我女神生日，我就係半島酒店book左自助餐，我見環境幾好就開左支紅酒飲，咁食食下我女神就無啦啦眼濕濕話而家屋企d口罩同d日用品所剩無幾，好擔心。我見時機成熟就隨即係枱底抽起兩條tempo廁紙，跟住同我女神講生日快樂，佢見到好開心話真係好多謝我如果冇呢兩廁紙，聽日柯完屎都唔知點算好。咁我見時機成熟，就向我女神表白，佢都願意做我女朋友，我真係好開心，我溝左佢咁多年終於成事。咁食完之後我就諗住打蛇隨棍上，係上便開左間房諗住有進一步行動，跟住佢話好似太快唔係幾好，我就即時係個袋到拎出兩盒3m 口罩出黎，我女神甜蜜蜜笑住咁就拖住我隻手上左去渡過一個甜蜜嘅夜晚。"},{"pid":"cc4e89f4c48132913e9ae62cfa09d084baa51025","tid":1864213,"uid":253984,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"打一大篇廢話都冇人理佢真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dac92f53321a0f418dbf878affd3c4502993b83","tid":1864213,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4e89f4c48132913e9ae62cfa09d084baa51025","tid":1864213,"uid":253984,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"打一大篇廢話都冇人理佢真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌"},{"pid":"9c61e75c4330b1d77dcce106f08740db2e38203d","tid":1864213,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dac92f53321a0f418dbf878affd3c4502993b83","tid":1864213,"uid":30